\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 This is so critical and NO your parents didn't pay me to say this.\uc0\u8232 \
\pard\tx1660\tx2160\pardeftab720\li2160\fi-2160\partightenfactor0
\ls5\ilvl2\cf2 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u9642 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 But there is way more at stake in you doing whatever super restrictive ridiculous thing you don't want to do.\uc0\u8232 \
\ls5\ilvl2\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u9642 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 And I want to be clear here...this doesn't mean do anything illegal...don't steal for your parents or smoke pot because they said it was ok...it's not!\uc0\u8232 \
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\partightenfactor0
\ls5\ilvl1\cf2 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u9702 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 What it does refer to though are things that your parents want you to do and you don't\uc0\u8232 \
\ls5\ilvl1\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u9702 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 In fact here is how I want to say it.\uc0\u8232 \
\ls5\ilvl1\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u9702 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Obedience starts where agreement ends\uc0\u8232 \
\pard\tx1660\tx2160\pardeftab720\li2160\fi-2160\partightenfactor0
\ls5\ilvl2\cf2 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u9642 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Meaning if you obey your parents 'most' of the time what that means is probably you're not really ever obeying them.\'a0 \uc0\u8232 \
\ls5\ilvl2\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u9642 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 You're just doing the things you don't really care about or worry about or are not passionate about\uc0\u8232 \
\ls5\ilvl2\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u9642 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 But when it comes to the important things you do what you want.\uc0\u8232 \
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\partightenfactor0
\ls5\ilvl1\cf2 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u9702 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 But here is why this is so important...\uc0\u8232 \
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\partightenfactor0
\ls5\ilvl1\cf3 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u9702 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec3 Your ability to obey your 
\f1\b EARTHLY
\f0\b0  father/mother will strengthen your ability to obey your 
\f1\b HEAVENLY
\f0\b0  father\cf2 \strokec2 \uc0\u8232 \
