\ls5\ilvl2\cf5 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u9642 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec5 And you've never thought about it like that or connected those dots but they are there\cf2 \strokec2 \uc0\u8232 \
\ls5\ilvl2\cf5 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u9642 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec5 Meaning when you get older there will be things that your heavenly father will ask you to do and you won't want to do that either.\cf2 \strokec2 \uc0\u8232 \
